('Jaime Segura & Associates', 'Tax and Accounting', 'Full-service tax, accounting and legal firm with over 15 years of experience serving English-speaking individuals and businesses across Spain. Specializing in tax advisory, accounting services, business setup, payroll, and comprehensive financial compliance for sole traders, freelancers, and international companies. Offers nationwide coverage with offices in Madrid, Granada, Marbella, and Málaga. Provides personalized service with clear communication in English, including online tax return handling and multilingual support via phone, email, Skype, and WhatsApp. Also offers legal services including conveyancing, business law, immigration, wills and inheritance, labor relations, and civil law.', 'Calle María de Molina, 54 – 5ª Planta', 'Madrid', 'Madrid', '+34 958 993 804', 'info@jaimesegura-associates.com', 'https://www.jaimesegura-associates.com', true, false, false, false, NOW(), NOW());
